snippet.title: 7DRL-Challenge 2017: They Look Strange And Have To Die - Developer Commentary
snippet.description:
I'm just talking a bit about my entry for the 7-Day-Roguelike-Challenge 2017. You can download it on https://ratking.itch.io/they-look-strange

The music was created by my brother Johannes-Paul Hanisch.
